// src/pages/DashboardPage.jsx
import React, { useEffect } from 'react';
import { useSelector, useDispatch } from 'react-redux';
import { 
  Container, 
  Grid, 
  Typography, 
  Box, 
  Paper, 
  Button,
  Card,
  CardContent,
  LinearProgress,
  Chip
} from '@mui/material';
import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom';
import { 
  School, 
  TrendingUp, 
  Timer, 
  Star,
  PlayArrow,
  Leaderboard as LeaderboardIcon
} from '@mui/icons-material';
import { fetchChallenges, fetchUserProgress } from '../store/challengeSlice';
import LoadingSpinner from '../components/common/LoadingSpinner';
import ChallengeMap from '../components/challenges/ChallengeMap';
import { getRank, getScoreColor, calculateProgress } from '../utils/helpers';

const DashboardPage = () => {
  const navigate = useNavigate();
  const dispatch = useDispatch();
  const { user } = useSelector(state => state.auth);
  const { challenges, userProgress, loading } = useSelector(state => state.challenges);

  useEffect(() => {
    dispatch(fetchChallenges());
    dispatch(fetchUserProgress());
  }, [dispatch]);

  if (loading) {
    return (
      <Box className="flex-center" style={{ minHeight: '60vh' }}>
        <LoadingSpinner message="Loading dashboard..." />
      </Box>
    );
  }

  // Calculate stats
  const completedChallenges = challenges?.filter(c => c.is_completed) || [];
  const totalChallenges = challenges?.length || 0;
  const averageScore = completedChallenges.length > 0 ? 
    Math.round(completedChallenges.reduce((sum, c) => sum + (c.best_score || 0), 0) / completedChallenges.length) : 0;
  const progressPercentage = calculateProgress(completedChallenges.length, totalChallenges);
  const userRank = getRank(completedChallenges.length, userProgress?.totalScore || 0);
  const nextChallenge = challenges?.find(c => !c.is_completed && c.is_unlocked);

  return (
    <Container maxWidth="xl">
      <Box sx={{ py: 4 }}>
        {/* Header */}
        <Box className="text-center" sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
          <Typography variant="h3" component="h1" gutterBottom>
            Learning Dashboard
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="h6" color="text.secondary" gutterBottom>
            Welcome back, {user?.username || 'Student'}! Track your progress and continue learning.
          </Typography>
          
          <Chip
            label={userRank}
            color="primary"
            sx={{ mt: 2, fontSize: '1.1rem', py: 2 }}
          />
        </Box>

        {/* Progress Overview Cards */}
        <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                <School sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'primary.main', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: 'primary.main' }}>
                  {completedChallenges.length}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Challenges Completed
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary">
                  out of {totalChallenges}
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                <Star sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: getScoreColor(userProgress?.totalScore || 0), mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: getScoreColor(userProgress?.totalScore || 0) }}>
                  {userProgress?.totalScore || 0}
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Total Score
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary">
                  points earned
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                <TrendingUp sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: getScoreColor(averageScore), mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: getScoreColor(averageScore) }}>
                  {averageScore}%
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Average Score
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary">
                  across all attempts
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>

          <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
            <Card sx={{ bgcolor: 'background.paper', height: '100%' }}>
              <CardContent sx={{ textAlign: 'center', p: 3 }}>
                <Timer sx={{ fontSize: 48, color: 'info.main', mb: 2 }} />
                <Typography variant="h4" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold', color: 'info.main' }}>
                  {progressPercentage}%
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Progress
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary">
                  overall completion
                </Typography>
              </CardContent>
            </Card>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* Progress Bar */}
        <Card sx={{ mb: 6, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <CardContent>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center', mb: 2 }}>
              <Typography variant="h6">
                Learning Progress
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body1" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                {completedChallenges.length} / {totalChallenges} completed
              </Typography>
            </Box>
            <LinearProgress 
              variant="determinate" 
              value={progressPercentage} 
              sx={{ 
                height: 12, 
                borderRadius: 6,
                bgcolor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)',
                '& .MuiLinearProgress-bar': {
                  borderRadius: 6
                }
              }} 
            />
            <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mt: 1, display: 'block' }}>
              Keep going! You're making great progress in your robotics journey.
            </Typography>
          </CardContent>
        </Card>

        {/* Next Challenge Recommendation */}
        {nextChallenge && (
          <Card sx={{ mb: 6, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
            <CardContent>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                🎯 Recommended Next Challenge
              </Typography>
              <Grid container spacing={3} alignItems="center">
                <Grid item xs={12} md={8}>
                  <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                    Challenge {nextChallenge.id}: {nextChallenge.title}
                  </Typography>
                  <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                    {nextChallenge.description}
                  </Typography>
                  <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', gap: 1 }}>
                    <Chip 
                      label={nextChallenge.difficulty || 'Beginner'} 
                      size="small" 
                      color="primary" 
                    />
                    <Chip 
                      label={`~${nextChallenge.estimated_time || 30} min`} 
                      size="small" 
                      variant="outlined" 
                    />
                  </Box>
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={12} md={4} sx={{ textAlign: 'center' }}>
                  <Button
                    variant="contained"
                    size="large"
                    startIcon={<PlayArrow />}
                    onClick={() => navigate(`/challenge/${nextChallenge.id}`)}
                    fullWidth
                  >
                    Start Challenge
                  </Button>
                </Grid>
              </Grid>
            </CardContent>
          </Card>
        )}

        {/* Quick Actions */}
        <Grid container spacing={4} sx={{ mb: 6 }}>
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper', textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                All Challenges
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                View and access all available robotics challenges.
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="contained"
                size="large"
                fullWidth
                onClick={() => {
                  // Scroll to challenges section
                  document.getElementById('challenges-section')?.scrollIntoView({ 
                    behavior: 'smooth' 
                  });
                }}
              >
                Browse Challenges
              </Button>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
          
          <Grid item xs={12} md={6}>
            <Paper sx={{ p: 3, bgcolor: 'background.paper', textAlign: 'center' }}>
              <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
                Leaderboard
              </Typography>
              <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 2 }}>
                See how you rank against other students.
              </Typography>
              <Button
                variant="outlined"
                size="large"
                startIcon={<LeaderboardIcon />}
                onClick={() => navigate('/leaderboard')}
                fullWidth
              >
                View Rankings
              </Button>
            </Paper>
          </Grid>
        </Grid>

        {/* Recent Activity */}
        <Card sx={{ mb: 6, bgcolor: 'background.paper' }}>
          <CardContent>
            <Typography variant="h6" gutterBottom>
              Recent Activity
            </Typography>
            {completedChallenges.length > 0 ? (
              <Grid container spacing={2}>
                {completedChallenges.slice(-6).reverse().map((challenge) => (
                  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4} key={challenge.id}>
                    <Paper 
                      sx={{ 
                        p: 2, 
                        bgcolor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.05)', 
                        cursor: 'pointer',
                        '&:hover': { bgcolor: 'rgba(255,255,255,0.1)' }
                      }}
                      onClick={() => navigate(`/challenge/${challenge.id}`)}
                    >
                      <Typography variant="subtitle1" sx={{ fontWeight: 'bold' }}>
                        Challenge {challenge.id}
                      </Typography>
                      <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary" sx={{ mb: 1 }}>
                        {challenge.title}
                      </Typography>
                      <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', justifyContent: 'space-between', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                        <Chip
                          label={`${challenge.best_score || 0}%`}
                          size="small"
                          sx={{ 
                            backgroundColor: getScoreColor(challenge.best_score || 0),
                            color: 'white',
                            fontWeight: 'bold'
                          }}
                        />
                        <Typography variant="caption" color="text.secondary">
                          Completed
                        </Typography>
                      </Box>
                    </Paper>
                  </Grid>
                ))}
              </Grid>
            ) : (
              <Box className="text-center" sx={{ py: 4 }}>
                <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary">
                  No completed challenges yet.
                </Typography>
                <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                  Start your first challenge to see your activity here!
                </Typography>
              </Box>
            )}
          </CardContent>
        </Card>

        {/* Challenges Section */}
        <Box id="challenges-section">
          <Typography variant="h4" gutterBottom className="text-center">
            All Challenges
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" color="text.secondary" className="text-center" sx={{ mb: 4 }}>
            Choose from a variety of robotics challenges designed to build your skills progressively
          </Typography>
          
          <ChallengeMap challenges={challenges} />
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Container>
  );
};

export default DashboardPage;
